<br><span style="display:none"> (<span class="bday">1940-11-28</span>) </span>November 28, 1940<span class="noprint ForceAgeToShow"> (age 84)</span><br><div style="display:inline" class="birthplace">
<a href="/wiki/Concord,_New_Hampshire" title="Concord, New Hampshire">Concord</a>, <a href="/wiki/New_Hampshire" title="New Hampshire">New Hampshire</a>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Nationality</th>
<td class="infobox-data category"><a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
